{"tid":1888112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公務員留家工作延長至3月1日","createTime":"2020-02-20T04:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T07:44:25.000Z","uid":23707,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"48d89a53bcf9139bfe9f722214b1a0c7c96fe90b","tid":1888112,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"一般打工仔：屌你老母"},{"pid":"09fe26452f8bc4558743b41af30e46adff70252c","tid":1888112,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"公務員又成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2a48746a1bec01ef1c1f925d20b899063f42c4","tid":1888112,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0fd56efe5278ead6dc821dd56e75726bf32303","tid":1888112,"uid":52701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"係延長特別上班安排，唔係在家工作安排"},{"pid":"e43e6411bbdb6cd27b67915eecc63c7ffdc77a91","tid":1888112,"uid":83265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"55dafce97aa5181b496882bc4949c3722b75bfe4","tid":1888112,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/20/P2020022000293.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F20%2FP2020022000293.htm&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=27b0fe94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/20/P2020022000293.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府延長特別上班安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  政府發言人今日（二月二十日）表示，因應疫情最新情況，政府會繼續實施部門的特別上班安排至三月一日，以減低社交接觸和病毒在社區傳播的風險。政府屆時會再檢視情況。<br />\n<br />\n  政府部門除了會繼續為市民提供緊急或必須的公共服務，以及維持有限度的基本服務外，亦會作出必要調整，向市民提供適切服務，並為逐步恢復正常服務作好準備。<br />\n<br />\n  但目前防控疫情仍是重中之重的工作，政府會密切注視疫情的發展，再作出下一步的決定和部署。<br />\n<br />\n  個別部門會就各項服務最新安排，盡快另行作出公布。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月20日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間12時00分"},{"pid":"aef9788c48ebbccf024f8c6f7cf41989f03db374","tid":1888112,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"應該最後一星期？？"},{"pid":"9fd9824cf661ba6f87ba60cbfdf63f92eee66c5c","tid":1888112,"uid":121196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"21/2/2020(五)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗</span></span>恐襲七個月 靜坐<br />\n<br />\n時間：19:30<br />\n地點：元朗黨鐵站/Yoho Mall<br />\n自備：口罩 文宣<br />\n<br />\n#21FEB20 #元朗 #七二一 #集會 #靜坐 #新界西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAyupn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAyupn5.jpg&h=bbdb7892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n21/2/2020(五)<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港仔</span></span> 勿忘721．七個月靜坐<br />\n<br />\n時間：20:00<br />\n地點：香港仔中心<br />\n自備：口罩 文宣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/southern_scout/6130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsouthern_scout%2F6130&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=5c165e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/southern_scout/6130</a><br />\n<br />\n#21FEB20 #香港仔 #七二一 #集會 #靜坐 #港島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BELXygx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBELXygx.jpg&h=ef34ab36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n21/2/2020(五)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">銅鑼灣</span></span> 毋忘惡襲．七個月靜坐<br />\n<br />\n時間：19:00<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣黨鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/cwbnow/456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcwbnow%2F456&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=27906658\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cwbnow/456</a><br />\n<br />\n#21FEB20 #銅鑼灣 #七二一 #集會 #靜坐 #港島<br />